peerAccountId.description: Account ID of EC2 Transit Gateway to peer with. Defaults to the account ID the AWS provider is currently connected to.

tags.description: Key-value tags for the EC2 Transit Gateway Peering Attachment. If configured with a provider `default_tags` configuration block present, tags with matching keys will overwrite those defined at the provider-level.

tagsAll.description: A map of tags assigned to the resource, including those inherited from the provider `default_tags` configuration block.
